        username - - the user who did the purchase
        cityname - - the city the user purchased
        type - - type of purchase
        date - - data the purchase was done
        expidate - - the expiry date of the purchase
        renew - - represents the number of times user renew the current purchase
        views - - represents the number of times the user watched the collection of maps
        downloads - - represents the number of times the user downloaded the collection of maps of this purchase
        price - - the price the user paid for this purchase
